Thirteenth session 
</b>Agenda item 1  
<b>Organizational and procedural matters 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Draft report of the Human Rights Council on its 
thirteenth session</b>*<b> 
</b><i>Vice-President and Rapporteur</i>: Mr. Hisham <b>Badr</b> (Egypt) 
</p>
<p>  
</p>
<p> * The text of resolutions and decisions adopted by the Human Rights Council will be available on the 
website of the Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Human Rights and will be 
subsequently included in part one of the final report. 
</p>

