<p><b>118</b> GE.10-17042 
</p>
<p><b>  C&#244;te d&#8217;Ivoire 
</b></p>
<p>778. At the 30th meeting, on 18 March 2010, the Council adopted draft decision 13/108 
without a vote (for the text as adopted, see part one, chapter II). 
</p>
<p><b>  Portugal 
</b></p>
